name: tzDropz Platinum PASS
description:
tzDropz is a community of PASS holders that grants you early access to future tzDropz exclusive NFTs

- Exclusive NFT drops

- Private community chat and announcements
- REVENUE SHARE of PASS ROYALTIES for DIAMOND PASS holders.

- tzDropz PASSES come in 4 tiers with the Silver being the entry-level

3 Gold -> 1 Platinum
3 Platinum -> 1 DIAMOND

The Basics: You would need to collect 27 total Silver PASSES to swap to a Diamond PASS

- There will only ever be 10k Diamond Passes in existence
- Diamond PASS holders additional benefits
-- Revenue Share program
-- Exclusive tzDropz NFTs directly air-dropped to each Diamond holder.

Visit our website below for a detailed list of benefits for each PASS tier, also follow us on Twitter, Discord, and Telegram to take part in regular giveaways!
